column5: WOW check this out  NOKIA SWEEPSTAKES PROMOTION  Congratulations!!Your email I.D was selected , you have won the sum of 750,000 Pounds Sterlings from Nokia Online 2009 promotion. Contact the Agent email below for further instructions.  dang lets go fishing and here I thought I would never win anything I will order my new truck and boat on the weekend
Good and get one of them sno-bears so we can ride up the lake in comfort this winter..
as soon as I receive the money you bet a done deal
Oh ye of little faith.  JF
Jeeez and I entered my e-mail address and did not win.  Congrats

Do you need to be a United Kingdom resident to accept a prize paid out in Pounds?  And did you actually sign up for something? Sounds like the email when my lost relative needed $2,000 to release my inheritance from my uncle I've never heard of. lol
Do we have the same uncle??
are you my sister?

Yup - As soon as all my money comes in (from just about every country in the world), I'll be handing in my resignation.  It's all ready, so I check my mailbox daily and just wait for the money to come rolling in.  Won't be long now.
I guess this means that you are going to replace those blades on your auger! Congrats man! Maybe a new Wally Bomber as well! LMAO! HH
can i borrow some?
You should forward that to everyones email lol
dang I find out it's a scam and here I bought some new stuff already  and  did already buy a new auger  and no you can't borrow some    LOL
Does that mean the imfamous Wally Diver is available! HH
love my wally diver it is always in the  lure rotation when all else fails use a wally diver
Ill buy that auger off ya for a good price....
LOL. I think I will keep the new one but I will be selling my old one, when the ice comes
I own a 10" 3 hp Strikemaster. I was just looking for a good/new cheap back up....
c'mon, not a scam - haven't you ever heard "you need to spend money to make money"? I suggest you give them whatever they want so they'll free up those pounds sterling for you
JUST AMAGINE.HAHAHAHAHA
